<li id="cite_note-21"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Psalms&amp;verse=6:5&amp;src=NKJV" class="external text" title="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Psalms&amp;verse=6:5&amp;src=NKJV" rel="nofollow">Psalms 6:5</a> and <a href="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Psalms&amp;verse=88:3-12&amp;src=NKJV" class="external text" title="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Psalms&amp;verse=88:3-12&amp;src=NKJV" rel="nofollow">Psalms 88:3-12</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Psalms&amp;verse=139:8&amp;src=NKJV" class="external text" title="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Psalms&amp;verse=139:8&amp;src=NKJV" rel="nofollow">Psalms 139:8</a>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Psalms&amp;verse=88:10&amp;src=NKJV" class="external text" title="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Psalms&amp;verse=88:10&amp;src=NKJV" rel="nofollow">Psalms 88:10</a>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-24"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Luke&amp;verse=22:15&amp;src=NKJV" class="external text" title="http://bibref.hebtools.com/?book=%20Luke&amp;verse=22:15&amp;src=NKJV" rel="nofollow">Luke 22:15</a>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-25"><b><a href="#cite_ref-25" title="">^</a></b> 1 Corinthians 11:26.</li>
